[[File:Kragen chathead.png|left|Kragen]]
'''Kragen''' is the farmer of the [[allotment]] patch south-east of [[Hemenster]]. He will watch after the player's allotments in exchange for certain items. The player receives four [[snowdrop seed]]s from Kragen as part of the [[Garden of Tranquillity]] quest.

==Shop==
Kragen also sells basic farming tools, which can be accessed by talking to him and asking ''Can you sell me something?'' It is not an actual shop and it has no set stock; each item must be bought individually through the dialogue.
